Package tagrelator.collect.flickr

Class Summary
FlickrCollector with this class you can connect to the Flickr API, search for Photos, and collect some data from the photos in the search results.
MyPhoto  
MyPhotoV2 reimplementation of the MyPhoto class, to minimize memory need
Searchterm  
SearchtermList a simple holder class used by the FlickrCollector and FlickrReader class it is basically a HashMap, but for storage reasons it got a class wrapped around for easy access to Searchterm objects by the String version of the Searchterm

SearchtermV2 reimplementation of Searchterm class for more compact memory
